<i> ♫ Listening to the temple's monk ringing the bell ♫</i>

17
00:01:00.700 --> 00:01:02.510
<i> ♫ Laying at the Mount Nan loft relaxing ♫</i>

18
00:01:02.510 --> 00:01:03.850
<i>♫ For you I hid my tears ♫</i>

19
00:01:03.850 --> 00:01:07.800
<i>♫ Abandoned worldly affairs. I will find you no matter 
the time and place ♫</i>

20
00:01:07.800 --> 00:01:11.460
<i>♫ It's you for the rest of my life. I want to be closer to you ♫</i>

21
