00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:54.360
<i> [Love Is All] </i>

31
00:01:54.360 --> 00:01:57.080
<i>[Tan LIngyin returns to Phoenix Mountain; 
Zheng Shaofeng figures out Zhou Zhengdao's secret]</i>

32
00:02:04.820 --> 00:02:07.820
It's currently county office working hours. Sir Tang,

33
00:02:07.820 --> 00:02:11.910
you are a salaried official so you shouldn't disappoint the imperial court.

34
00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:14.120
Don't go.

35
00:02:14.120 --> 00:02:15.170
What?

36
00:02:15.170 --> 00:02:18.420
You're already here, so let's not waste time.

37
00:02:18.420 --> 00:02:21.570
Sit.


39
00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.300
What are you doing?

40
00:02:34.300 --> 00:02:35.880
Dissecting you.

41
00:02:35.880 --> 00:02:38.100
Are you crazy?

42
00:02:44.100 --> 00:02:47.730
What are you doing? Even if you want to break up, you don't need to use a knife! 
 <i>[Mortuary]</i>

43
00:02:47.730 --> 00:02:50.680
If you want to be with Jiang Muchun, you can just go!

44
00:02:50.680 --> 00:02:53.400
Isn't this how it's written in your stories?

45
00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:57.940
You can marry whoever you want. On your wedding day, I'll be sure to send you my blessings.

46
00:02:57.940 --> 00:03:01.810
"Wishing you a loving and lasting marriage; A harmonious relationship makes every day blossom."

47
00:03:01.810 --> 00:03:03.550
How about that?

48
00:03:04.500 --> 00:03:09.880
You wrote in your stories that you have to dissect their heart in order to truly understand them.

49
00:03:11.890 --> 00:03:15.100
Don't raise a knife when you're saying sweet things.

50
00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:22.480
Whatever, I'll teach you next time. I'm leaving.

51
00:03:23.790 --> 00:03:25.710
The moon is really round tonight.

52
00:03:25.710 --> 00:03:27.380
Really?

53
00:03:30.490 --> 00:03:32.130
It is!

54
00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:39.140
What are you doing?

55
00:03:39.140 --> 00:03:41.390
Lo-Lo-Lo-Looking at the moon.

56
00:03:41.390 --> 00:03:45.300
<i> ♫ I am so, so, so captivated by you like this ♫ </i>

57
00:03:45.300 --> 00:03:48.760
It's only because you wanted me to look, not that I wanted to stay.

58
00:03:48.760 --> 00:03:51.970
<i>♫ I want to work hard to gain your attention ♫</i>

59
00:03:51.970 --> 00:03:55.400
<i> ♫ Laying in your embrace ♫</i>

60
00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:59.380
The moon is so beautiful tonight. Let's not waste it.

61
00:03:59.380 --> 00:04:01.030
What else?

62
00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:06.700
<i> ♫ I want to accompany you to go catch the wind ♫</i>

63
00:04:06.700 --> 00:04:11.480
<i> ♫ Daydreaming together, a dream we cannot wake up from ♫</i>

64
00:04:11.480 --> 00:04:14.320
I won't kiss someone else's man.

65
00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:19.500
Are you jealous of others?

66
00:04:19.500 --> 00:04:21.820
Others?

67
00:04:21.820 --> 00:04:26.250
What others? Do you not know their names? Others, others, others, who are the others?

68
00:04:26.250 --> 00:04:30.400
Jiang Muchun. She approached us with a motive.

69
00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:34.050
Before finding out her motive, you can't be careless.

70
00:04:34.670 --> 00:04:38.500
What motive can she have? Isn't it just to marry you?

71
00:04:38.500 --> 00:04:41.530
It's not that simple. Other than the emperor,

72
00:04:41.530 --> 00:04:45.820
nobody knows that Tang Feilong is Tang Tianyuan. How does she know?

73
00:04:45.820 --> 00:04:51.110
Also, why did she appear right at this time?

74
00:04:51.110 --> 00:04:56.000
It's probably because she asked the emperor. She's your fiancée after all.

75
00:04:56.700 --> 00:05:01.320
A fiancée should be waiting at home for her lover to return.

76
00:05:01.320 --> 00:05:04.110
There's no way she doesn't understand this concept.

77
00:05:04.980 --> 00:05:08.900
So what? She probably couldn't wait.

78
00:05:08.900 --> 00:05:13.060
Plus, who says women have to be passive and just wait?

79
00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:16.790
You're taking her side?

80
00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:23.650
Jiang Muchun is good at everything. Everyone in the county office likes her.

81
00:05:23.650 --> 00:05:29.500
What about me? I can't do anything and I only cause trouble. How can I compare to her?

82
00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:31.910
If you keep talking, I'm going to change my mind.

83
00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:38.940
It's true.

84
00:05:39.700 --> 00:05:43.740
Jiang Muchun likes you and I'm not in a position to make her stay away from you.

85
00:05:43.740 --> 00:05:46.680
On this matter, you also have to decide for yourself.

86
00:05:52.300 --> 00:05:57.030
I also don't know how to stay calm when I'm facing you two.

87
00:05:57.860 --> 00:06:02.620
So I think we should separate for a while.

88
00:06:02.620 --> 00:06:04.680
Until you've thought it through.

89
00:06:05.940 --> 00:06:08.100
I was joking!

90
00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:11.350
Think about it.

91
00:06:12.050 --> 00:06:14.350
Don't even think about standing on both boats! 
 <i>(T/N: two-timing)</i>

92
00:06:16.650 --> 00:06:19.830
You said Miss Ruyi was abandoned.

93
00:06:19.830 --> 00:06:23.480
Then... Then how did she become your younger cousin?

94
00:06:23.990 --> 00:06:25.800
This...

95
00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:29.930
My father pitied her so he took her in.

96
00:06:29.930 --> 00:06:33.550
But he was afraid that Aunt would be upset so he left her to be raised by another family.

97
00:06:33.550 --> 00:06:37.350
He would only send money, clothes, and food regularly.

98
00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:44.950
Her late father that she mentioned... is that her adoptive father?

99
00:06:47.490 --> 00:06:49.950
She grew up as a beggar.

100
00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:57.740
She's so pitiful. So pitiful.

101
00:07:12.430 --> 00:07:14.160
Head Constable Zheng.

102
00:07:16.930 --> 00:07:18.500
Head Constable Zheng!

103
00:07:22.110 --> 00:07:23.750
Head Constable Zheng!

104
00:07:33.760 --> 00:07:36.870
You can't eat this, it's for Miss Ruyi.

105
00:07:41.140 --> 00:07:42.580
Whatever.

106
00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:56.830
Look at this.

107
00:07:59.700 --> 00:08:02.960
This... was supposed

108
00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:06.890
to be eaten by Miss Ruyi and me while we enjoyed the moonlight.

109
00:08:09.500 --> 00:08:13.650
It's a shame that it's useless now.

110
00:08:13.650 --> 00:08:15.630
Help me throw it away.

111
00:08:46.600 --> 00:08:49.510
Who uses stir-fried chili and meat as a filling?

112
00:08:51.360 --> 00:08:53.320
But I still need to thank you.

113
00:08:54.140 --> 00:08:57.930
This is the first time someone made mooncakes for me.

114
00:09:01.020 --> 00:09:04.760
Sorry, this is the last time.

115
00:09:16.510 --> 00:09:20.680
Duan Feng! Duan Feng, I'm here!

116
00:09:20.680 --> 00:09:22.700
Duan Feng?

117
00:09:26.330 --> 00:09:28.870
Why is the door open?

118
00:09:32.010 --> 00:09:33.910
Who cares.

119
00:09:33.910 --> 00:09:36.750
Duan Feng, I brought good wine and meat.

120
00:09:36.750 --> 00:09:40.220
Wake up!

121
00:09:41.090 --> 00:09:45.690
Duan Feng... Duan Feng, are you dead? Duan Feng!

122
00:09:49.390 --> 00:09:52.070
- You...
- I haven't married you yet, I can't die.

123
00:09:52.070 --> 00:09:54.080
Liar. You can't die before telling me.

124
00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:55.230
What did you bring?

125
00:09:55.230 --> 00:09:57.970
The good wine and meat you wanted. Can you tell me now?

126
00:09:57.970 --> 00:10:00.310
<i>Guards, Adviser Tan's going to take Duan Feng and escape!</i>

127
00:10:00.310 --> 00:10:02.080
<i>Block them! Don't let them escape.</i>

128
00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:04.210
- W-What's the meaning of this? 
- Let's go!

129
00:10:04.210 --> 00:10:05.280
Where are we going?

130
00:10:05.280 --> 00:10:08.670
They're already claim that I've escaped. If I stay, then won't I be wrongly accused?

131
00:10:08.670 --> 00:10:11.720
Let's go. Hurry, hurry, hurry!

132
00:10:17.290 --> 00:10:19.580
I didn't unlock the door. Let's go back quickly!

133
00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:21.250
Go back and let them capture me?

134
00:10:21.250 --> 00:10:24.850
If we don't go back, then we really will be guilty of breaking out.

135
00:10:24.850 --> 00:10:28.180
Idiot. Can't you tell that someone's trying to harm you? Hold on tight.

136
00:10:28.180 --> 00:10:31.230
Listen to me! If we go and find Sir Tang now, he'll have a solution.

137
00:10:31.230 --> 00:10:34.600
Does the county office belong solely to Sir Tang?

138
00:10:38.410 --> 00:10:40.480
Where is he? What's going on?

139
00:10:40.480 --> 00:10:43.060
This morning, right after changing shifts,

140
00:10:43.060 --> 00:10:46.560
I was knocked out by someone from behind.

141
00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:51.320
When I woke up, I bumped into Adviser Tan and Duan Feng escaping,

142
00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:54.000
then they took the horses and left.

143
00:10:58.640 --> 00:11:02.010
Head Constable Zheng, it really wasn't me being careless.

144
00:11:02.010 --> 00:11:04.860
Tongling has always been peaceful.

145
00:11:04.860 --> 00:11:06.900
I never thought this would happen.

146
00:11:06.900 --> 00:11:10.050
Tongling is the least peaceful place. You should shut your mouth.

147
00:11:14.850 --> 00:11:17.020
This lock... was opened by a key.

148
00:11:17.020 --> 00:11:20.170
Recently, only Adviser Tan frequently comes to the prison.

149
00:11:20.170 --> 00:11:22.700
Also, she...

150
00:11:22.700 --> 00:11:26.170
Also, she brought a key.

151
00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:34.320
- Have you seen Zhou Zhengdao? 
 - No.

152
00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:36.690
Head Constable Zheng!

153
00:11:38.090 --> 00:11:40.710
Zhou Zhengdao, come out!

154
00:11:40.710 --> 00:11:44.600
Who is it? Miss Ruyi?

155
00:11:46.230 --> 00:11:47.530
What's all this commotion this morning?

156
00:11:47.530 --> 00:11:49.160
Your adviser took Duan Feng away.

157
00:11:49.160 --> 00:11:51.140
Oh no, she was taken by Duan Feng.

158
00:11:51.140 --> 00:11:52.350
Get your words straight before speaking.

159
00:11:52.350 --> 00:11:53.860
Look at the time!  Why are you still caring about this!

160
00:11:53.860 --> 00:11:56.170
Hurry, get your horse and people, and go!

161
00:12:03.730 --> 00:12:04.960
Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!

162
00:12:04.960 --> 00:12:07.160
- Hurry! 
 - Scram!

163
00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:10.330
Hurry! Hurry!

164
00:12:24.540 --> 00:12:26.730
Chase them!

165
00:12:29.870 --> 00:12:32.030
Hurry, chase them!

166
00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:36.550
Did you wash your hands? They stink.

167
00:12:36.550 --> 00:12:38.990
Is there time to talk about this right now?

168
00:12:38.990 --> 00:12:41.270
I just saved your life.

169
00:12:41.270 --> 00:12:45.500
Do you know who knocked you out? Was it the guards?

170
00:12:45.500 --> 00:12:50.100
Someone drugged my food. They probably wanted to silence me after I escaped.

171
00:12:50.100 --> 00:12:52.880
Luckily, you came to deliver food,

172
00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:56.550
so they could coincidentally implicate you in this mess.

173
00:12:56.550 --> 00:13:00.570
This way, I'm a fugitive and you're an accomplice. Neither of us can escape.

174
00:13:00.570 --> 00:13:02.430
Did you offend any gangs?

175
00:13:02.430 --> 00:13:05.660
What gangs? I am the gang.

176
00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:11.320
Someone must've been unhappy that I was caught in your hands and wanted me dead.

177
00:13:11.320 --> 00:13:14.130
What did you actually do?

178
00:13:14.130 --> 00:13:18.930
I'm just a bandit committing a crime. Do the authorities need to make such a deliberate plan?

179
00:13:18.930 --> 00:13:22.590
I think that this has something to do with the gold mine case.

180
00:13:22.590 --> 00:13:27.040
You were still saying that you know nothing about the gold mine case. Let's just go and find Sir Tang.

181
00:13:27.040 --> 00:13:30.920
Why can't you understand? Tang Feilong won't listen to me.

182
00:13:30.920 --> 00:13:33.590
But he would listen to me.

183
00:13:49.610 --> 00:13:51.600
Hey!

184
00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:58.370
Hero Duan, get out of the way!

185
00:14:02.900 --> 00:14:05.990
- Hurry! 
 - Get on!

186
00:14:06.410 --> 00:14:10.010
Move away! Move away!

187
00:14:23.790 --> 00:14:26.510
Oh, you're a hero?

188
00:14:26.510 --> 00:14:30.770
I've been around in the pugilistic world, just robbing from the rich and giving to the poor.

189
00:14:30.770 --> 00:14:32.260
It's their casual nickname for me.

190
00:14:32.260 --> 00:14:34.860
What are you going to do now? You can't keep running, Hero Duan.

191
00:14:34.860 --> 00:14:37.980
I'm already used to it, but you have to get used to it.

192
00:14:37.980 --> 00:14:39.700
Once we get up the mountain, I'll tell you everything.

193
00:14:39.700 --> 00:14:42.040
Really? You've said it so don't trick me!

194
00:14:42.040 --> 00:14:44.470
- Why would I trick you? 
 - Stop!

195
00:14:46.510 --> 00:14:48.610
Tang Tianyuan.

196
00:14:52.170 --> 00:14:55.040
A good dog doesn't block the way. Hurry and move aside.

197
00:14:55.040 --> 00:14:57.870
I will think about keeping her alive.

198
00:14:57.870 --> 00:15:00.310
If you hurt her even a little,

199
00:15:00.310 --> 00:15:03.430
I won't let you leave here alive.

200
00:15:03.430 --> 00:15:06.310
Let's see which is faster: your arrow or my sword.

201
00:15:06.310 --> 00:15:08.750
Do you get any benefits from killing her?

202
00:15:08.750 --> 00:15:12.020
Do I get any benefits from staying in your prison?

203
00:15:12.540 --> 00:15:14.390
I would rather have a quick death,

204
00:15:14.390 --> 00:15:16.870
- and have this woman accompany me on the way. 
 - Don't you dare!

205
00:15:16.870 --> 00:15:18.920
See if I dare or not.

206
00:15:18.920 --> 00:15:23.640
I'm just afraid that you won't bear the pain of being separated from your lover forever.

207
00:15:29.790 --> 00:15:31.840
Am I right?

208
00:15:31.840 --> 00:15:34.000
Hurry up and get me three thousand taels.

209
00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:37.210
If anyone tries to block me, I'll kill your adviser immediately.

210
00:15:37.210 --> 00:15:39.660
You won't bear to do that.

211
00:15:39.660 --> 00:15:41.370
What?

212
00:15:41.860 --> 00:15:44.970
Didn't we agree that we would be a fairytale couple?

213
00:15:44.970 --> 00:15:46.590
We would spend our lives together happily

214
00:15:46.590 --> 00:15:49.030
and have a bunch of kids?

215
00:15:49.030 --> 00:15:50.000
Are you crazy?

216
00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:53.520
Yes! I'm lovesick for you. It's incurable.

217
00:15:53.520 --> 00:15:56.650
Sir Tang, please give us our freedom.

218
00:15:56.650 --> 00:15:59.160
Tan Lingyin, what are you saying?

219
00:16:01.050 --> 00:16:03.700
True love is found only in adversity.

220
00:16:03.700 --> 00:16:07.470
I now know that Duan Feng is my one true love.

221
00:16:08.290 --> 00:16:12.820
I will follow him and dissect his heart. Did you hear that?

222
00:16:12.820 --> 00:16:13.830
Dissect my heart!

223
00:16:13.830 --> 00:16:16.600
Dissect his heart!

224
00:16:20.100 --> 00:16:23.730
Move aside and let them go.

225
00:16:27.030 --> 00:16:29.430
<i> [Be of good virtue and diligent] </i>

226
00:16:41.890 --> 00:16:46.760
Sir, it's getting dark. Here's a lamp.

227
00:17:04.420 --> 00:17:06.690
If you have something to say, go ahead.

228
00:17:11.200 --> 00:17:12.690
Sir,

229
00:17:12.690 --> 00:17:16.700
Adviser Tan has found her love. This time,

230
00:17:16.700 --> 00:17:19.980
she left with him willingly.

231
00:17:19.980 --> 00:17:22.360
Sir, you should let her go, too.

232
00:17:22.360 --> 00:17:27.480
Bandits are prevailing in Tongling. The gold mine case is complicated and unpredictable.

233
00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:33.000
If Sir Jiang really loves you,

234
00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:36.770
he wouldn't tell you to stay by my side and get into this mess.

235
00:17:40.730 --> 00:17:45.100
This letter explains everything clearly.

236
00:17:48.200 --> 00:17:52.290
I believe that Sir Jiang will definitely understand.

237
00:17:53.720 --> 00:17:56.650
Sir, are you kicking me out?

238
00:17:57.960 --> 00:18:01.660
The carriage is ready. You can leave anytime.

239
00:18:07.940 --> 00:18:10.520
Why can't you understand my feelings?

240
00:18:10.520 --> 00:18:13.820
This is the jade bracelet you gave me when you were younger.

241
00:18:13.820 --> 00:18:18.890
Since I put it on, I've been unwilling to take it off.

242
00:18:18.890 --> 00:18:23.240
Even if I had innumerable jewels, they cannot compare to it.

243
00:18:23.970 --> 00:18:28.900
When I wear it, it's as if you are always with me.

244
00:18:30.770 --> 00:18:35.650
I know... that you definitely care for me.

245
00:18:36.090 --> 00:18:38.860
It's just temporary...

246
00:18:38.860 --> 00:18:42.510
You've temporarily been seduced by another woman so you can't think clearly.

247
00:18:42.510 --> 00:18:44.750
It's okay.

248
00:18:44.750 --> 00:18:49.530
Why are you bothered if I'm not even bothered?

249
00:18:52.340 --> 00:18:56.450
I wasn't the one who gave this bracelet to you.

250
00:18:57.590 --> 00:19:00.250
Sir, do you not remember?

251
00:19:00.250 --> 00:19:03.120
This is what you gave me when we were young, after we fell in love at first sight.

252
00:19:03.120 --> 00:19:06.560
Old Madam specifically had this pair of jade accessories made for us.

253
00:19:06.560 --> 00:19:12.160
One piece is your jade pendant, the other is my jade bracelet.

254
00:19:12.160 --> 00:19:14.470
This piece of jade was found by my mother.

255
00:19:14.470 --> 00:19:19.190
It is uncommonly clear, so it was made into this pendant of mine.

256
00:19:20.270 --> 00:19:22.190
But...

257
00:19:23.370 --> 00:19:26.290
she made a decision without my authority

258
00:19:26.290 --> 00:19:28.340
and without my knowledge

259
00:19:28.340 --> 00:19:31.230
to make and give you this bracelet.

260
00:19:31.940 --> 00:19:34.140
Are you saying

261
00:19:36.670 --> 00:19:41.530
that this bracelet was from Old Madam?

262
00:19:43.550 --> 00:19:46.020
It can't be.

263
00:19:46.020 --> 00:19:48.680
This was given to me by Xi Hulu at that time.

264
00:19:48.680 --> 00:19:50.560
It definitely represents your intentions.

265
00:19:50.560 --> 00:19:54.220
Xi Hulu is someone who runs errands for the Tang family.

266
00:19:54.220 --> 00:19:58.500
He's not very bright and he doesn't speak clearly.

267
00:19:58.500 --> 00:20:00.680
If it's...

268
00:20:00.680 --> 00:20:03.180
because of his mistake that made you misunderstand,

269
00:20:03.180 --> 00:20:06.750
I'll apologize on his behalf.

270
00:20:15.350 --> 00:20:16.750
Also...

271
00:20:17.460 --> 00:20:19.800
My heart already belongs to another.

272
00:20:22.830 --> 00:20:27.550
If all this time, you've been ruminating about this jade pendant,

273
00:20:27.550 --> 00:20:29.550
then you can have it.

274
00:20:30.470 --> 00:20:32.180
I don't want it.

275
00:20:34.010 --> 00:20:35.750
I don't want it!

276
00:20:39.810 --> 00:20:41.610
<i>[Miaosheng Restaurant]</i>

277
00:20:48.200 --> 00:20:49.800
You're awake?

278
00:20:53.020 --> 00:20:56.450
I was just patrolling on the street and when I turned my head,

279
00:20:56.450 --> 00:20:59.170
I happened to see you snoring on the street.

280
00:20:59.170 --> 00:21:03.680
No matter how bad it is being here in Zhu Dacong's place, it's still better than being on the street.

281
00:21:07.190 --> 00:21:11.350
I... was affected by the wind and got dizzy.

282
00:21:11.350 --> 00:21:15.350
I went out for a walk just now. Maybe I fainted.

283
00:21:22.190 --> 00:21:25.810
Don't worry.

284
00:21:25.810 --> 00:21:29.750
Zhao Xia changed your clothes and Xi He cleaned you up.

285
00:21:30.510 --> 00:21:33.970
I've been watching you all afternoon.

286
00:21:33.970 --> 00:21:38.240
Why don't you make some space for me and let me lie down for a bit?

287
00:21:38.240 --> 00:21:40.350
I'm so sleepy.

288
00:21:42.750 --> 00:21:45.910
Fine, I'll lie here then.

289
00:21:53.240 --> 00:21:55.160
Zheng Shaofeng...

290
00:22:03.670 --> 00:22:07.060
In the future, you have to tell me

291
00:22:07.060 --> 00:22:11.340
if there's anything wrong. Do you hear me?

292
00:22:13.660 --> 00:22:18.530
I... I'm a bit sleepy. I want to sleep a little longer.

293
00:22:22.860 --> 00:22:24.390
Sleep then.

294
00:22:40.910 --> 00:22:44.570
<i>[Meet in the backyard at midnight]</i>

295
00:22:59.170 --> 00:23:01.180
<i>[Phoenix Village]</i>

296
00:23:02.170 --> 00:23:06.190
He's back! Brothers! Boss is back!

297
00:23:11.230 --> 00:23:14.820
Brothers! Let's wish eternal happiness

298
00:23:14.820 --> 00:23:15.730
for our boss and his wife!

299
00:23:15.730 --> 00:23:17.800
- Eternal happiness! 
 - Eternal happiness!

300
00:23:17.800 --> 00:23:20.220
Happiness, my foot! Shut up! 
 <i>[Courage and loyalty]</i>

301
00:23:20.220 --> 00:23:23.630
My brothers, I'm very touched that

302
00:23:23.630 --> 00:23:27.430
you didn't disperse but waited for my return while I was in trouble.

303
00:23:27.430 --> 00:23:30.770
I'm also touched that you didn't rush down the mountain and break me out of prison.

304
00:23:31.310 --> 00:23:33.450
What touched me the most...

305
00:23:36.040 --> 00:23:38.070
is this woman.

306
00:23:39.490 --> 00:23:42.510
<i>- Let's go, let's go! 
- Stop hanging about.</i>

307
00:23:42.510 --> 00:23:45.560
Let's go! Stop hanging around.

308
00:23:45.560 --> 00:23:47.640
<i>Let's go! Let's go!</i>

309
00:23:47.640 --> 00:23:51.060
Why are you touching me when we can talk properly?

310
00:23:51.060 --> 00:23:53.180
Don't forget what you promised me.

311
00:23:54.470 --> 00:23:57.780
You've been working at the county office for some time already, haven't you?

312
00:23:57.780 --> 00:24:01.120
Why are you still so naive? What happened in prison was one thing.

313
00:24:01.120 --> 00:24:05.870
Of course, things are different now that we're in my territory.

314
00:24:05.870 --> 00:24:10.040
Don't tell me you... still want to leave the mountain easily?

315
00:24:10.040 --> 00:24:11.310
What do you mean?

316
00:24:11.310 --> 00:24:12.340
Do you trust me?

317
00:24:12.340 --> 00:24:14.080
No.

318
00:24:14.080 --> 00:24:17.210
Then don't blame me for forcing you to swear to the heavens.

319
00:24:21.390 --> 00:24:22.990
What are you doing?

320
00:24:22.990 --> 00:24:25.330
<i>[Courage and loyalty]</i>

321
00:24:25.330 --> 00:24:27.170
I, Duan Feng...

322
00:24:27.900 --> 00:24:30.510
- Say your name.
 - No.

323
00:24:30.510 --> 00:24:31.610
I'll kill you if you don't.

324
00:24:31.610 --> 00:24:33.440
I won't even if you do.

325
00:24:35.560 --> 00:24:37.270
You, Tan Lingyin!

326
00:24:38.030 --> 00:24:40.220
Stop playing, okay? I can't marry you.

327
00:24:40.220 --> 00:24:43.210
From today onwards, we will be sworn brothers!

328
00:24:43.210 --> 00:24:48.990
We will care for each other in life and death; share wealth and misfortune; Heaven and Earth are our witnesses.

329
00:24:55.290 --> 00:24:58.060
I was able to return thanks to you this time.

330
00:24:58.060 --> 00:25:01.140
I grew up in the pugilistic world so I repay my debts.

331
00:25:01.140 --> 00:25:05.210
Since you're not willing to marry me, then we'll become sworn brothers.

332
00:25:10.810 --> 00:25:15.550
I'll give you a big present in celebration of our new brotherhood.

333
00:25:16.260 --> 00:25:18.010
Boss. 
 <i>[Miaosheng Restaurant]</i>

334
00:25:18.010 --> 00:25:22.340
Three months is almost over. Are we still running this restaurant?

335
00:25:23.950 --> 00:25:26.260
No matter how many Miaosheng Restaurants we open,

336
00:25:26.260 --> 00:25:29.140
my wife's true heart will not be given in return.

337
00:25:31.970 --> 00:25:35.700
Boss, I think the wind is getting stronger.

338
00:25:35.700 --> 00:25:40.420
It's a sign that my wife is thinking of me.

339
00:25:54.050 --> 00:25:57.060
<i>Our Madam recently found a rare jade.</i>

340
00:25:57.060 --> 00:25:59.700
<i>One half was made into a pendant and the other half into a bracelet. </i>

341
00:25:59.700 --> 00:26:02.010
<i>The pendant has been taken by our young master.</i>

342
00:26:02.010 --> 00:26:04.250
<i>Xi Hulu is just an errand boy for the Tang family.</i>

343
00:26:04.250 --> 00:26:08.750
<i>He's not sharp. If his mistake caused you any misunderstanding...</i>

344
00:26:20.560 --> 00:26:22.510
I saved you...

345
00:26:23.610 --> 00:26:26.120
Yet you hurt me.

346
00:26:28.340 --> 00:26:31.730
Do I have to make you go through some pain

347
00:26:32.410 --> 00:26:36.830
so you can know who truly loves you?

348
00:26:57.430 --> 00:26:59.390
<i>Xue Li, what are you doing?</i>

349
00:26:59.390 --> 00:27:02.600
<i>Sir's hand was bitten by a bug. I'm going to treat his bite.</i>

350
00:27:02.600 --> 00:27:04.320
Xue Li.

351
00:27:07.020 --> 00:27:10.220
Miss Jiang, did you call me?

352
00:27:25.790 --> 00:27:27.230
<i>[Miaosheng Restaurant]</i>

353
00:27:55.260 --> 00:27:56.900
It sounded so good.

354
00:28:00.760 --> 00:28:05.580
Ruyi, have you heard the story about Boqi consuming dreams? 
 <i>(T/N: Boqi is a mythical creature)</i>

355
00:28:07.750 --> 00:28:12.380
Legend says that the beast Boqi loves to eat nightmares.

356
00:28:12.380 --> 00:28:16.520
Children don't have nightmares when Boqi is by their side.

357
00:28:18.870 --> 00:28:22.290
I made a new scent packet for you.

358
00:28:22.290 --> 00:28:25.150
Boqi is embroidered on it.

359
00:28:25.800 --> 00:28:30.190
You won't have nightmares if you keep it with you day and night.

360
00:28:38.830 --> 00:28:42.570
Ruyi, I'm serious.

361
00:28:43.780 --> 00:28:45.880
I can protect you.

362
00:28:47.410 --> 00:28:50.940
You can also rely on me.

363
00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:10.810
I'm not sleeping!

364
00:29:10.810 --> 00:29:13.410
It's me, not Sir.

365
00:29:15.510 --> 00:29:20.110
The nights are cooler as autumn approaches. You need to wear more layers when on night duty.

366
00:29:23.310 --> 00:29:25.200
Is Sir Tang asleep?

367
00:29:25.200 --> 00:29:27.980
Not yet. I just helped him apply his medicine.

368
00:29:29.340 --> 00:29:32.280
<i>[Tongling County Office]</i>

369
00:29:40.200 --> 00:29:41.570
Sir.

370
00:29:50.100 --> 00:29:53.870
Sir... Tan Baba needs to eat.

371
00:29:53.870 --> 00:29:58.010
You have to eat, too. You haven't eaten anything today.

372
00:29:58.010 --> 00:30:01.300
I'm not hungry. You can go and eat.

373
00:30:01.300 --> 00:30:04.870
That won't do. Adviser left clear instructions before she left.

374
00:30:04.870 --> 00:30:08.680
The three meals a day need to be organized clearly for you.

375
00:30:11.450 --> 00:30:16.600
I wonder if Adviser Tan... has eaten yet.

376
00:30:25.400 --> 00:30:27.490
What happened to your hand?

377
00:30:27.490 --> 00:30:31.280
The weather has been so hot lately, so there are a lot of mosquitoes.

378
00:30:31.280 --> 00:30:35.880
Xiang Gua and Xue Li have helped me apply ointment already.

379
00:30:37.700 --> 00:30:40.020
Sir, do you think...

380
00:30:40.890 --> 00:30:42.530
Sir!

381
00:30:43.550 --> 00:30:45.170
Sir!

382
00:30:46.300 --> 00:30:48.860
<i>Help! Sir has fainted!</i>

383
00:30:48.860 --> 00:30:52.290
<i>Sir! Sir! What happened to you?</i>

384
00:30:52.290 --> 00:30:56.300
<i>Sir! Sir!</i>

385
00:31:03.020 --> 00:31:08.570
Adviser! Adviser, save me! Hurry and save me! I'm going to die!

386
00:31:08.570 --> 00:31:10.600
He was being suspicious in our mountains!

387
00:31:10.600 --> 00:31:15.010
Tan Lingyin, is this what you mean by sincerity? You sent a spy over?

388
00:31:15.010 --> 00:31:18.610
No, I didn't. Xi Hulu, what are you doing here?

389
00:31:18.610 --> 00:31:22.700
Adviser, Sir is in trouble. He fainted.

390
00:31:22.700 --> 00:31:23.570
What?

391
00:31:23.570 --> 00:31:26.840
Sir is going to die! What am I going to do?

392
00:31:26.840 --> 00:31:30.800
That's great! You can regret your decision now to avoid becoming a widow.

393
00:31:30.800 --> 00:31:32.800
Shut up!

394
00:31:33.500 --> 00:31:34.460
Tell me.

395
00:31:34.460 --> 00:31:36.940
- He was fine when I left. 
 - I also don't know why.

396
00:31:36.940 --> 00:31:39.000
Sir just fainted suddenly.

397
00:31:39.000 --> 00:31:42.970
I'm afraid he won't make it so I came here to look for you.

398
00:31:42.970 --> 00:31:45.800
- Where are you going? 
 - I'm going to find him!

399
00:31:45.800 --> 00:31:49.810
I knew you came here under a pretense! Tell me the truth. Why did you come?

400
00:31:49.810 --> 00:31:51.660
I purposely told him to let us go.

401
00:31:51.660 --> 00:31:53.860
It was to get close to you and gain your trust.

402
00:31:53.860 --> 00:31:57.300
What's the point of earning a bandit's trust?

403
00:31:57.300 --> 00:32:01.260
Whether or not we can successfully solve the gold case depends on you.

404
00:32:05.080 --> 00:32:07.600
I know that you don't want to hurt me.

405
00:32:07.600 --> 00:32:11.470
Otherwise, there would be a bunch of constables here today.

406
00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:18.130
Let me ask you. Do you really trust him?

407
00:32:19.550 --> 00:32:22.600
Okay, go.

408
00:32:29.400 --> 00:32:30.800
Thank you.

409
00:32:32.640 --> 00:32:36.800
But can you do me another favor?

410
00:32:38.300 --> 00:32:42.600
If I help, does that mean I can choose whether you give me

411
00:32:42.600 --> 00:32:45.880
ten thousand pieces of gold, luxury mansions, or beautiful women?

412
00:32:45.880 --> 00:32:48.370
There's no gold, luxury mansions, or beautiful women.

413
00:32:48.370 --> 00:32:50.640
Then, what benefit do I get?

414
00:32:50.640 --> 00:32:54.640
Justice and fairness. The refugees who died wrongly can rest in peace.

415
00:33:02.430 --> 00:33:04.150
Go!

416
00:33:05.730 --> 00:33:07.830
- Adviser, you're back. 
 - Adviser.

417
00:33:13.720 --> 00:33:17.060
This person... I've seen him before.

418
00:33:19.730 --> 00:33:21.700
Where was it again?

419
00:33:28.700 --> 00:33:30.980
Sir! Sir!

420
00:33:30.980 --> 00:33:32.750
You scared me.

421
00:33:32.750 --> 00:33:34.180
What's going on?

422
00:33:34.180 --> 00:33:35.340
Why are you back?

423
00:33:35.340 --> 00:33:40.280
Xi Hulu said you fainted so I didn't feel like acting anymore. Does it hurt?

424
00:33:43.270 --> 00:33:47.940
Please could this masked hero put down my carved Ruyao vase.

425
00:33:56.330 --> 00:33:59.930
How are you sick? To me, you are still as annoying as ever.

426
00:33:59.930 --> 00:34:02.000
Du-Duan Feng?

427
00:34:02.000 --> 00:34:05.510
Don't get excited. I just came to take a look. I'm leaving soon.

428
00:34:05.510 --> 00:34:06.650
What did the doctor say?

429
00:34:06.650 --> 00:34:10.020
The doctor said that somebody missed you so much he got sick.

430
00:34:10.020 --> 00:34:11.290
Talk properly.

431
00:34:11.290 --> 00:34:13.900
He was overworked and overly anxious.

432
00:34:13.900 --> 00:34:15.130
What else?

433
00:34:15.130 --> 00:34:19.990
It's nothing serious. They're just exaggerating. Don't worry.

434
00:34:25.000 --> 00:34:27.680
Which quack told you that you worked too much?

435
00:34:28.370 --> 00:34:31.790
Do you constantly experience numbness and spasms in your arms?

436
00:34:31.790 --> 00:34:34.350
Also, do you often feel that your body is not within your control?

437
00:34:35.800 --> 00:34:38.600
I swear to the heavens, I didn't say it.

438
00:34:38.600 --> 00:34:42.130
This kind of poison is called strychnine. It's also known as Qianji poison.

439
00:34:42.130 --> 00:34:46.630
Sir, did you touch anything dirty with your hands?

440
00:34:51.220 --> 00:34:55.820
This is it. Sang Jie used this to kill the refugees.

441
00:34:55.820 --> 00:35:00.830
Sir, it looks like someone wants to kill you without anyone noticing.

442
00:35:01.530 --> 00:35:03.550
Where did you get this medicine?

443
00:35:05.550 --> 00:35:09.320
Xue Li has been with me since childhood. She wouldn't poison me.

444
00:35:11.420 --> 00:35:13.520
You two should leave first.

445
00:35:14.520 --> 00:35:17.450
I want to have a private chat with this doctor.

446
00:35:19.510 --> 00:35:20.830
<i>[Long day]</i>

447
00:35:20.830 --> 00:35:22.510
Brother Zhou!

448
00:35:24.190 --> 00:35:26.430
Where is he?

449
00:35:42.100 --> 00:35:45.050
<i>The books have been organized, bring them to Sir Tang later.</i>

450
00:35:45.050 --> 00:35:46.000
<i>All right.</i>

451
00:35:46.000 --> 00:35:50.380
<i>Also, does our county office require any purchases recently? Bring those over, too.</i>

452
00:35:50.380 --> 00:35:53.520
<i>- All right, no problem. 
 - Okay.</i>

453
00:35:56.710 --> 00:35:58.310
Head Constable Zheng.

454
00:36:00.270 --> 00:36:05.880
I waited for you for a long time. Let's go now.

455
00:36:20.100 --> 00:36:22.710
Those who were involved in mining were mostly refugees.

456
00:36:22.710 --> 00:36:25.650
Everyone's neck was marked with an ink tattoo.

457
00:36:25.650 --> 00:36:29.100
So you're also a refugee. How did you escape?

458
00:36:29.100 --> 00:36:34.410
Old Tie was Sang Jie's housekeeper and the one responsible for hiding the gold.

459
00:36:34.410 --> 00:36:37.170
He told me Sang Jie would kill us.

460
00:36:37.170 --> 00:36:41.700
So we decided to take a chance and run away with the gold.

461
00:36:41.700 --> 00:36:45.940
My mission was to lead the refugees who survived

462
00:36:45.940 --> 00:36:49.490
to the mountains before Sang Jie noticed and form a gang.

463
00:36:49.490 --> 00:36:53.040
Then find an opportunity to save Old Tie?

464
00:36:54.100 --> 00:36:56.520
Where is this person?

465
00:36:56.520 --> 00:36:58.280
<i>Sir.</i>

466
00:37:04.370 --> 00:37:06.700
Sir, I'm here to apply medicine for you.

467
00:37:06.700 --> 00:37:11.460
This county office is truly different. Even servants are this pretty.


469
00:37:30.800 --> 00:37:35.580
<i> ♫ The overnight spring breeze, as I go out into the world,  
hoping not to disappoint ♫</i>

470
00:37:35.580 --> 00:37:41.800
<i> ♫ To roam the world, just this ferry of longing, I can't let go ♫</i>

471
00:37:41.800 --> 00:37:45.900
<i> ♫  The ferry keeps floating, but the way back seems endless ♫</i>

472
00:37:45.900 --> 00:37:50.400
<i> ♫ The chilling waters brought a lonely boat that caught my eye ♫</i>

473
00:37:50.400 --> 00:37:55.300
<i> ♫ A fierce horse, where is it going in this mortal world? ♫</i>

474
00:37:55.300 --> 00:38:01.600
<i> ♫ Where can I leisurely see to the limit of the cloud and stars ♫</i>

475
00:38:01.600 --> 00:38:06.760
<i> ♫ On an ancient road, as the sun sets,
 I asked the young bamboo ♫</i>

476
00:38:06.760 --> 00:38:10.800
<i> ♫ When will you reply? ♫</i>

477
00:38:10.800 --> 00:38:14.150
<i> ♫ Only when you come here boundless ♫</i>

478
00:38:14.150 --> 00:38:20.600
<i> ♫ Can you drink till drunk ♫</i>

479
00:38:20.600 --> 00:38:24.140
<i> ♫ To also leave boundless ♫</i>

480
00:38:24.140 --> 00:38:26.810
<i> ♫ Freely pick a song  ♫</i>

481
00:38:26.810 --> 00:38:30.100
<i> ♫ A good dream, a youth’s travels ♫</i>

482
00:38:30.100 --> 00:38:36.880
<i> ♫  The swaying shadows from the candle and 
longings are still the same as that year’s ♫</i>

483
00:38:36.880 --> 00:38:40.500
